Package net.objectzoo.ebc.test

This package contains two mock object action implementations that can be used to test EBCs.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    MockAction<T>
    The MockAction is an Action implementation that can be used in (unit) tests to collect the results of a tested EBC.
    MockAction0
    The MockAction0 is an Action0 implementation that can be used in (unit) tests to count the signals of a tested EBC.
